<!-- /**
* Defines a .NET web project using the Microsoft.NET.Sdk.Web SDK.
*
* @param {string} Sdk - Specifies the SDK to use for the project.
* @param {object} PropertyGroup - Defines a set of properties for the project.
* @param {string} TargetFramework - Specifies the target framework for the project.
* @param {string} Nullable - Enables nullable reference types for the project.
* @param {string} ImplicitUsings - Enables implicit namespace imports for the project.
* @param {object} ItemGroup - Defines a set of items for the project.
